---
---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Intro">
	<h1>Design engineer</h1>
	<p class="tagline">
		Happiest in the space between <em>make it beautiful</em> and <code>make it work</code>
	</p>
	<p class="support">
		Graphic-design roots and 7+ years building accessible, interactive experiences for the
		web — with an eye for the details most people scroll right past.
	</p>
	<a class="cta" href="#projects">See what I've made</a>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		max-width: calc(var(--measure) + var(--space-4) * 2);
		margin-inline: auto;
		padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-4);
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: var(--text-display);
		line-height: var(--leading-tight);
		letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
		font-weight: 500;
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		line-height: var(--leading-normal);
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
	}

	.tagline em {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.tagline code {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.85em;
		line-height: 1;
		background: var(--green-tint);
		color: var(--green-ink);
		padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-2);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.support {
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		line-height: var(--leading-normal);
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		max-width: var(--measure);
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-8);
	}

	.cta {
		display: inline-block;
		background: var(--green-ink);
		color: var(--bg);
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		font-weight: 500;
		padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.cta:hover {
		opacity: 0.85;
	}

	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
		.cta {
			transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
		}
	}
</style>
